A4.text: Uber Technologies, Inc. is an American multinational transportation company that provides ride-hailing services, courier services, food delivery, and freight transport.

A5.text: Uber is publicly traded on the New York Stock Exchange under the ticker symbol UBER. It is headquartered in San Francisco, California, and operates in approximately 70 countries and 15,000 cities worldwide.
